  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>Sea Flavso" likely refers to "Machhli Flavors of the Sea" . It serves a variety of cuisines including Chinese, Malwani, Thai, and North Indian, as well as desserts and beverages</p>
        <p>The restaurant is known for its extensive menu, quality food, and excellent service, with some reviews mentioning tamper-proof packaging. It is not a vegetarian-only restaurant and is not known to serve buffet or alcohol. </p>
        <p> Some popular dishes include sizzlers, kebabs, and mocktails. It also offers a variety of flavors from coastal cuisine. The restaurant is known for its relaxed atmosphere and live music. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="https://www.fashiontvluxeresort.com/media/3nciodg0/fashiontv-luxe-resort-restoranlar-alacarte-seafood-restaurant-list-card.jpg">
      </div>
